---

<section
    id="positive-beer"
    class="relative text-[#e7e5e4] font-serif min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-12 md:py-24 border-b border-emerald-900/10"
>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div
            class="order-2 md:order-1 relative h-[400px] bg-gradient-to-b from-amber-950/40 to-[#0c0a09] rounded-lg border border-amber-900/30 p-8 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
        >
            <div
                class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_120%,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-amber-900/20 via-transparent to-transparent"
            >
            </div>

            <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden opacity-60">
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-8 left-[15%] w-3 h-3 bg-amber-400/40 rounded-full animate-[float_3s_ease-in-out_infinite]"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-12 left-[25%] w-2 h-2 bg-amber-300/30 rounded-full animate-[float_4s_ease-in-out_infinite_0.5s]"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-6 left-[35%] w-4 h-4 bg-amber-500/50 rounded-full animate-[float_3.5s_ease-in-out_infinite_1s]"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-10 left-[45%] w-2 h-2 bg-amber-400/35 rounded-full animate-[float_4.5s_ease-in-out_infinite_1.5s]"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-14 left-[55%] w-3 h-3 bg-amber-300/40 rounded-full animate-[float_3.8s_ease-in-out_infinite_0.8s]"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-8 left-[65%] w-2 h-2 bg-amber-500/30 rounded-full animate-[float_4.2s_ease-in-out_infinite_1.2s]"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-16 left-[75%] w-3 h-3 bg-amber-400/45 rounded-full animate-[float_3.3s_ease-in-out_infinite_0.3s]"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-10 left-[85%] w-2 h-2 bg-amber-300/35 rounded-full animate-[float_4.8s_ease-in-out_infinite_1.8s]"
                >
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-amber-500/20 blur-3xl rounded-full"></div>
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        class="w-32 h-32 text-amber-500/60 relative"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 013.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center space-y-2">
                    <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-amber-500/80 tracking-tight">C₂H₅OH</div>
                    <div class="text-xs tracking-[0.3em] text-amber-500/40 uppercase">Etanol</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="order-1 md:order-2 space-y-6">
            <span
                class="text-emerald-500/80 text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase block trigo-positive-chapter"
                >La Fiesta</span
            >
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4]">La Alegría Líquida</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-[#d6d3d1] leading-relaxed">
                Hay una teoría seria que dice que no domesticamos el trigo para hacer pan, sino para
                hacer cerveza.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base text-[#a8a29e] leading-relaxed">
                La fermentación nos dio una bebida segura (libre de bacterias) y rica en calorías.
                Pero más importante: nos dio la fiesta, el ritual y la cohesión social. La cerveza
                suavizó las fricciones de vivir juntos en grandes grupos.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    @keyframes float {
        0%,
        100% {
            transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
            opacity: 0;
        }
        10% {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        90% {
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        100% {
            transform: translateY(-400px) scale(0.5);
            opacity: 0;
        }
    }
</style>
